# Secrets — never commit
**/*.env
**/*.env.*
**/secrets*
**/credentials*
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/.npmrc
**/.netrc
**/.aws/
**/.gh-token
**/auth.json
**/*token*

# Negation: the documented placeholder template MUST ship (it is matched by
# `**/*.env.*` above, so re-include it AFTER the broad ignores — order matters).
!**/.env.example

# Dependencies / build artifacts
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
**/.vite/
**/coverage/

# OS / editor
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/

# Local runtime / scratch (never publish)
.tmp/
**/*.log
ai/tasks/*/tmp/
ai/tasks/*/.cache/
**/worktrees/

# Out-of-tree certification record (WP6): the certified SHA + final scan outputs
# are recorded here per-task and must NEVER be committed (it would self-reference
# the freeze commit it certifies).
ai/tasks/*/certification-record.local.md

# Review scratch (the commit itself is the diff)
*.diff
